      "message": "[Critical] Line 1486: Clearing `removed`/`erased` before the re-clone and sync complete can make a previously left conversation visible again even if the clone later fails, leaving stale membership/messages exposed as an active conversation. Defer reactivating the conversation until after the clone succeeds, or roll back these fields on every failure path.\n\n```suggestion\n        // Reactivate only after the clone/sync path has succeeded, or restore the\n        // previous removed/erased values if cloning fails.\n```",
