      "message": "Line 2009: For a removed group, an existing pending request is deleted before the duplicate-request check. This changes the previous behavior from ignoring duplicate requests to replacing the pending request with the latest inbound one, which can reset metadata such as sender/received time and allows request churn. Keep the existing request unless there is a concrete reason to replace it, or compare/update only when the new request is strictly newer/valid.\n\n```suggestion\n        if (pimpl_-\u003egetRequest(convId) !\u003d std::nullopt)\n            return;\n```",
